    <item>
      <title>A way of developing captcha based on ezcomments 1.0</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/ezcomments/forum/general/a_way_of_developing_captcha_based_on_ezcomments_1_0</link>
      <description>Hi,&#13;
&#13;
eZ Comments 1.0 doesn't support captcha. But it's possible to extend ezcomments to achieve captcha feature.&#13;
&#13;
There is one way which uses API of RECAPTCHA(http://projects.ez.no/recaptcha ), an ez publish extension, to implement the  captcha functionality based on ezcomments.&#13;
&#13;
Please click this link to get steps to do and example code: &#13;
http://issues.ez.no/IssueView.php?Id=16305&#13;
&#13;
Feel free to suggest other ways :)&#13;
&#13;
Best regards&#13;
Chen</description>
