    <item>
      <title>Some missing features</title>
      <link>http://projects.ez.no/ezcomments/forum/general/some_missing_features</link>
      <description>Hi&#13;
maybe these remarks are already in the roadmap or maybe I misse something in the extension. &#13;
&#13;
The user IP is not insert in the table (if the web sites in behind a CDN we should track the header  HTTP_X_FORWARDED_FOR )  &#13;
&#13;
For specific websites and legal reason, the comment can't be delete we must keep informations about the comment. The status columns should be use to display or not the comment in the front office.&#13;
&#13;
&#13;
&#13;
For moderation, &#13;
For specific websites (for kids), we must moderate the comment before is publication. (the status column can be use for this.)&#13;
It will be useful to be able to search a specific comments (by title/user name/status etc).&#13;
&#13;
Stephane&#13;
&#13;
&#13;
&#13;
</description>
